{"tid":1007002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"航班量創新高 港珠澳大橋農曆年酬賓免路費一星期","createTime":"2019-02-03T12:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T08:52:29.000Z","uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b47e849f26c3707423d603c11303b536ab1aa752","tid":1007002,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T12:26:47.000Z","msg":"隨着農曆新年臨近，香港國際機場航機數量再創高峯。民航處連續11日（1月23日至2月2日）每日處理超過2,300架次航機，昨日（2日）更處理了2,467架次航機，創下單日處理航機數量的新高，打破2017年8月24日超強颱風天鴿遠離香港後，機場恢復運作錄得的2,341架次紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【逼爆香港】內地客自由行來港辦年貨 團體屯門「趕客」促返深圳購物<br />\n<br />\n民航處在過去11日平均每日處理約2,380架次航機（包括所有在機場升降及過境航班），亦較去年同期每日平均2,265架次上升約5%。昨日處理包括1,226架次航機升降，以及1,241架次過境航班（創下單日最多過境航班紀錄）。民航處處長李天柱表示，已因應假期航班需求，調配額外人手當值，確保在農曆新年航班高峯期保持航空交通服務安全和暢順有序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190203/59219540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190203%2F59219540&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=8aa60842\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190203%2F59219540&h=7c872de1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190203/59219540</a>"},{"pid":"c0b5254ad7011c099fb77c7a2e356d16921f9dc4","tid":1007002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T14:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415026c461a1bb925c5d65f2f9a002f79921952e","tid":1007002,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T14:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxjqXDo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxjqXDo.png&h=cc5d91a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/prAUQYo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FprAUQYo.png&h=3b27e4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYV2fp3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYV2fp3.png&h=55043d21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPqYybK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPqYybK.png&h=4bc24799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無喇無喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n南下去西九既車飛, <br />\n車飛起碼要去到18號星期一(正月十四)先叫有得買<br />\n<br />\n中間係咪擺工停駛咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6ca0a25463079a9bcf5c46d53f0bcc638e08ac","tid":1007002,"uid":21378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T08:52:29.000Z","msg":"西九好少飛. 好多都係經深圳 來港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}